comments: Looney (GSW) brings his arm forward and marginal contact occurs with Porter Jr.'s (DEN) shoulder as they engage at the end of the drive.
Green (GSW) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Looney (GSW) grasps and quickly releases Gordon's (DEN) jersey and marginal contact occurs off-ball prior to the pursuit of the imminent pass.
Curry (GSW) cuts toward Porter Jr. (DEN) and avoids making body contact that affects his ability to defend.
Gordon (DEN) swipes down and avoids making arm contact with DiVincenzo (GSW) as he jumps verticality and absorbs the contact that occurs during the driving shot attempt.
DiVincenzo (GSW) is moving alongside Murray's (DEN) path and marginal body contact occurs during Murray's (DEN) drive.
Curry (GSW) reaches in and marginal contact occurs with Murray's (DEN) arm at the end of the drive.
While contesting the driving shot attempt, Looney (GSW) makes marginal contact with Brown's (DEN) off arm while he attempts to shield himself during the play.
Watson (DEN) and Green (GSW) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs.
Replay review of the shot clock violation called on Brown (DEN) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Correctly called 24 second violation.
After receiving the handoff, Murray (DEN) takes multiple steps prior to releasing his dribble.
Green (GSW) commits a take foul on Gordon (DEN).

Thompson (GSW) slightly extends his arm forward and marginal contact occurs with Brown's (DEN) arm as they come together at the end of the drive. While applying defensive pressure, Looney (GSW) legally ties up the ball with Brown.
Murray (DEN) legally contests Thompson's (GSW) jump shot, making marginal "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
